caption: This image shows a plate of food with bacon, bananas, and syrup. The bacon is cooked and crispy, while the bananas are sliced and topped with syrup. The plate is on a white surface, and there is a fork on the side.

The image shows two elephants standing on a rocky beach with trees in the background. One of the elephants is holding a small rock in its trunk while the other is standing next to it, looking at something on the ground.
